{"tid":358673,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"仆你個臭街 比個廢老對住我放屁","createTime":"2017-08-14T00:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T03:56:12.000Z","uid":89134,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88474c95268c1d40cbefe273716068020cd497d1","tid":358673,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T00:25:03.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死廢老 又行得咁撚慢<br />\n阻撚住哂 仲要突登放個勁撚響既屁<br />\n平日啲人話響屁唔臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你但係九成係因為班廢老特別構造 <br />\n個響屁係臭既<br />\n仲要連放幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到成程扶手電梯都聞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/14/082449_fe486994384a4e3ccc0b818f270152ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F14%2F082449_fe486994384a4e3ccc0b818f270152ff.jpg&h=304a1494&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c8668ffa124935640071a47d6fec6ea9a9ce03b","tid":358673,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T00:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146c77b00f527af2306511fad71e4c492be16a17","tid":358673,"uid":89985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T00:26:36.000Z","msg":"有畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bcd6924fdabdfdf7ff8322ee5ceac591a5e696c","tid":358673,"uid":135784,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T00:27:52.000Z","msg":"條扶手電梯幾長夠你聽到佢放再聞到再拎電話出嚟影"},{"pid":"a21f9c88af7b4521a3ff8fb9dbc66673bd9acb6f","tid":358673,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T00:31:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條扶手電梯幾長夠你聽到佢放再聞到再拎電話出嚟影</blockquote><br />\n唔係好長姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760f53c28ef7a1bab5e6a15b100132c82fea3d87","tid":358673,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T02:41:08.000Z","msg":"屌你老母我老豆黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放佢上黎把撚"},{"pid":"b69fb455c296b21e7a28ccecdda7657d598c7566","tid":358673,"uid":49033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T03:34:56.000Z","msg":"美國《時代雜誌》一篇引述英國艾希特大學（University of Exeter）研究的報導指出，臭屁中所含的硫化氫在微量時對身體有益，能活化細胞的粒腺體，幫助降低罹癌、失智、中風等疾病風險。學者已經研發出一種能發揮相同作用的化合物，將進行人體試驗。<br />\n<br />\n臭屁中含微量硫化氫　能保護細胞粒腺體<br />\n<br />\n屁的特殊氣味來自一種稱為硫化氫的化合物，而硫化氫正是細菌分解食物時產生的異味。此份研究的作者馬特懷特曼博士（Dr. Matt Whiteman）指出，受到疾病攻擊的細胞會吸收酵素，產生微量的硫化氫，而微量硫化氫能活化粒腺體、維持細胞活性。如果這個程序無法進行，細胞會死亡、身體即失去調節細胞存活與控制發炎反應的能力。<br />\n<br />\n參與研究的學者表示，雖然大量的硫化氫可能造成人體中毒，微量硫化氫則可以保護又被稱為「細胞能量工廠」的粒腺體，幫助降低罹患癌症、中風、心臟病、失智症等疾病風險。"},{"pid":"cf7e98dd5a715532ddb844330d5dd057064eac42","tid":358673,"uid":108356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T03:44:23.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 個屎眼用左6-70年 都唔比人抖下"},{"pid":"231c08200c8e0fb3a8e2e5cc9b8b91a702179963","tid":358673,"uid":116711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T03:56:12.000Z","msg":"樓主吸入高濃度硫化氫，<br />\n日內見頭暈，記得即call白車，否則...<br />\n下世小心d. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}